            <div class="main_r">
                <div class="tit_nav">
                    <span class="tit_l">您所在位置：</span><a href="/Home/Index">首页</a><b>></b><span>案例信息</span>
                </div>
                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/1323" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">HRM-0122</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8526 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">沉重的翅膀——飞行员辞职风波</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The Heavy Wings – Pilot Resignation Disturbances</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">许红军，张雷</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中国民航大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">华龙航空公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">交通运输业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">人力资源部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">11 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">飞行员；辞职；人员流动；民航；人力资源管理</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Pilots; resignation; staff turnover; Civil Aviation; human resources management</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">飞行员的合理有序流动，是中国民航业未来发展必须解决的问题之一。要离开的飞行员静坐、绝食、上访、与“东家”对簿公堂；不希望飞行员离职的航空公司就扣押飞行员证件、档案、索要天价赔偿金，这是中国民航飞行员流动乱象的真实写照。本案例描述了华龙航空公司在民航快速发展过程中，所面临的飞行员短缺和跳槽问题。随着中国民用航空业向民营资本开放和人力资源的市场化发展，航空公司业绩上的差异，导致员工收入差距拉大，产生攀比现象，一定程度上造成了飞行员的心里失衡。华龙航空公司虽在经营、管理、服务方面做出了一定努力，但市场意识不强，习惯了行政体制下飞行员的管理制度，按行政管理模式运作企业的痕迹比较明显，还依然以垄断的人才观束缚飞行员，引发了飞行员的抵触情绪，飞行员与航空公司的矛盾日益激化。因此，华龙航空公司如何转变用人观念，改革现有的管理模式，稳定飞行员队伍是其面临的巨大挑战。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">The rational and orderly turnover of pilots is one of the problems of China Civil Aviation industry，which should be solved during its development process in the future. The pilots choose sitting in protest, pastier, petitions, disputing with the airline in the court to resign; on the contrary, the airlines have to seize the pilots certificates, personal files and claim them for a large sum of money .That realistically descript the chaotic turnover of pilots. This case describes the shortage and job-hopping of pilots, which Hualong airlines encountered in the rapid development of civil aviation industry. With the capital liberalization and the development of human resources of China civil aviation industry, different airlines have made different performance. So the income gaps among pilots become wider, which caused them to a psychological imbalance in a certain extent. Hualong Airlines has made certain efforts in aspects of operation, management and service, however, it lack a strong market consciousness and has been conditioned to the administrative system of pilot management system. It is obvious that Hualong still runs in a administration model and control pilots by a HR view of talent monopoly, caused the pilots emotional conflict. The contradiction between the pilots and Hualong has intensified increasingly. Therefore, Hualong Airlines faces enormous challenges about how to change the idea, reform the existing management mode, and stabilize the pilots’ team.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2013</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《人力资源管理》、《管理学》、《组织行为学》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Price-Mueller员工离职模型、无固定期限劳动合同、员工心理契约及员工心理健康、核心员工管理理论、员工激励机制</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2013-10</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">查看全文:</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/1323" target="_blank">点击查看</a></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
